  "time_ut": 1657357833,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0d85\u0d9c\u0db8\u0dd0\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0db4\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2 \u0db1\u0dcf\u0dba\u0d9a \u0dbb\u0dd0\u0dc3\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dd3\u0db8\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dd0\u0db3\u0dc0\u0dba\u0dd2 - \u0db4\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dda\u0db1\u0dca\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dc0 \u0d9a\u0dd0\u0db3\u0dc0\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u0dad\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The Prime Minister calls a meeting of party leaders - also calls Parliament",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe has arranged to call a special emergency meeting of party leaders. The meeting of the party leaders has been called to discuss the current situation in the country as well as the future measures.",
        "In the meantime, he has also informed the Speaker to convene the Parliament as soon as possible."
      ],
